# Walkthrough: Initial Project Setup (School Management System)

I have successfully initialized the project structure and implemented the initial dashboard UI.

## Progress Overview
- [x] **Project Scaffolded**: Vite + React + TypeScript + Electron.
- [x] **Desktop Integration**: Configured Electron main and preload processes.
- [x] **Design System**: Integrated Tailwind CSS with a premium color palette.
- [x] **Initial Dashboard**: Created the core layout with sidebar, header, and statistics cards.

## Design Inspiration
I researched high-quality school management designs on Dribbble to ensure a premium look.

## Changes Made
### Configuration Files
- [package.json](file:///e:/WorkSpace/School/school-management-system/package.json): Defines dependencies and Electron scripts.
- [vite.config.ts](file:///e:/WorkSpace/School/school-management-system/vite.config.ts): Configured Vite to work with Electron.
- [tailwind.config.js](file:///e:/WorkSpace/School/school-management-system/tailwind.config.js): Custom design tokens (Indigo, Orange, Coral accents).

### Student Management Module
- [src/components/StudentList.tsx](file:///e:/WorkSpace/School/school-management-system/src/components/StudentList.tsx): Displays a searchable table of students with real-time data from the database.
- [src/components/StudentForm.tsx](file:///e:/WorkSpace/School/school-management-system/src/components/StudentForm.tsx): A premium modal form for registering new students, featuring real-time state management.
- **Integration**: The dashboard stats now update automatically whenever a new student is registered.

### Database Layer
- [electron/db.ts](file:///e:/WorkSpace/School/school-management-system/electron/db.ts): Initialized 10 core tables based on the approved schema.
- [electron/main.ts](file:///e:/WorkSpace/School/school-management-system/electron/main.ts): Core IPC bridge for data persistence.
- [src/services/db.ts](file:///e:/WorkSpace/School/school-management-system/src/services/db.ts): Frontend service layer.
- [src/App.tsx](file:///e:/WorkSpace/School/school-management-system/src/App.tsx): Main dashboard UI with:
    - Sidebar navigation (Tableau de bord, Élèves, etc.)
    - Stats cards (Total Élèves, Enseignants, etc.)
    - Recent activity table.

### Source Code
- [electron/main.ts](file:///e:/WorkSpace/School/school-management-system/electron/main.ts): Window management and IPC setup.

## Next Steps
1. **Database Setup**: Initialize SQLite for student and grade management.
2. **Student Module**: Implement the registration form and list view.
3. **Financial Module**: Create the cash management (Caisse) interface.
